<details class="faq-item">
    <summary class="faq-question">
        <span>How does the floating teleprompter work?</span>
        <svg class="faq-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" />
        </svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>
            CueCard creates a floating window that stays on top of all your apps. You can record videos, go live, or present while your notes remain visible only to you.
        </p>
    </div>
</details>

<details class="faq-item">
    <summary class="faq-question">
        <span>Can I use it with my camera app?</span>
        <svg class="faq-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" />
        </svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>
            Yes! CueCard floats over any app including your native camera, Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, and more.
        </p>
    </div>
</details>

